26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_engine_fifo_g84.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:31 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "nv50.h"
30#include "channv50.h"
31
32static void
33g84_fifo_uevent_fini(struct nvkm_fifo *fifo)
34{
35 struct nvkm_device *device = fifo->engine.subdev.device;
36 nvkm_mask(device, 0x002140, 0x40000000, 0x00000000);
37}
38
39static void
40g84_fifo_uevent_init(struct nvkm_fifo *fifo)
41{
42 struct nvkm_device *device = fifo->engine.subdev.device;
43 nvkm_mask(device, 0x002140, 0x40000000, 0x40000000);
44}
45
46static const struct nvkm_fifo_func
47g84_fifo = {
48 .dtor = nv50_fifo_dtor,
49 .oneinit = nv50_fifo_oneinit,
50 .init = nv50_fifo_init,
51 .intr = nv04_fifo_intr,
52 .pause = nv04_fifo_pause,
53 .start = nv04_fifo_start,
54 .uevent_init = g84_fifo_uevent_init,
55 .uevent_fini = g84_fifo_uevent_fini,
56 .chan = {
57 &g84_fifo_dma_oclass,
58 &g84_fifo_gpfifo_oclass,
59 NULL
60 },
61};
62
63int
64g84_fifo_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_fifo **pfifo)
65{
66 return nv50_fifo_new_(&g84_fifo, device, index, pfifo);
67}
